<item chapterid="599858" siteid="0" sourceid="0" sourcecid="0" sourcecorder="0" articleid="1933" articlename="神级小职员" volumeid="0" posterid="1" poster="admin" postdate="1521705212" lastupdate="1521705212" chaptername="第0章66805 477幕后操纵" chapterorder="477" size="6538" saleprice="0" salenum="0" totalcost="0" attachment="" summary="    四哥说：”你说的有道理，可是，他要是不知道此事呢？那岂不是没用？”

